{
  "script_id": "aliasing",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "aliasing",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/aliasing/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "看老电影时，你有没有发现飞驰的车轮竟然在倒转？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "aliasing",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/aliasing/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "车轮明明在往前，画面里却像在往后转，甚至静止不动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "aliasing",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/aliasing/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "这不是错觉，而是相机每秒只拍有限张画面造成的错位。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "aliasing",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/aliasing/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "这种高频信号伪装成低频的现象，就叫做混叠。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "aliasing",
      "section_id": "sample",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "sample-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/aliasing/xiaoxiao/sample-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "真实世界的信号是连续的，比如一条不停摆动的正弦曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "aliasing",
      "section_id": "sample",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "sample-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/aliasing/xiaoxiao/sample-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "要用数字记录它，只能每隔一小段时间取一个值，这就是采样。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "aliasing",
      "section_id": "sample",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "sample-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/aliasing/xiaoxiao/sample-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 28080,
      "text": "每秒取多少个点，叫做采样率，记作 fs。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "aliasing",
      "section_id": "undersample",
      "line_id": "under-1",
      "filename": "undersample-under-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/aliasing/xiaoxiao/undersample-under-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 30960,
      "text": "如果采样点太稀疏，就会漏掉波形中间的快速起伏。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "aliasing",
      "section_id": "undersample",
      "line_id": "under-2",
      "filename": "undersample-under-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/aliasing/xiaoxiao/undersample-under-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "把这些稀疏的点连起来，会得到一条完全不同的低频曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "aliasing",
      "section_id": "undersample",
      "line_id": "under-3",
      "filename": "undersample-under-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/aliasing/xiaoxiao/undersample-under-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "奈奎斯特定理告诉我们，采样率必须大于信号频率的两倍。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "aliasing",
      "section_id": "apparent",
      "line_id": "app-1",
      "filename": "apparent-app-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/aliasing/xiaoxiao/apparent-app-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.44,
      "size": 23040,
      "text": "混叠后看到的假频率，可以精确算出来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "aliasing",
      "section_id": "apparent",
      "line_id": "app-2",
      "filename": "apparent-app-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/aliasing/xiaoxiao/apparent-app-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "它等于真实频率减去采样率的整数倍，再取绝对值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "aliasing",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/aliasing/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "调高真实频率，或调低采样率，看红色假波如何出现。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "aliasing",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/aliasing/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "当采样率越过奈奎斯特这条线，红波就会和灰波重合。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "aliasing",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/aliasing/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "采样不足时，高频信号会伪装成低频，这就是混叠。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "aliasing",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/aliasing/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.83,
      "size": 29232,
      "text": "只要采样率高过频率的两倍，就能忠实还原原信号。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "aliasing",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/aliasing/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.45,
      "size": 23184,
      "text": "看懂了车轮倒转的秘密，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 33.10000000000001,
